                <br />
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-primary mt-2">Read More</a>
            </div>
        </article>

        <article class="card mb-3">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Gaming Tips for Cat Owners</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Practical strategies to keep your gaming experience smooth and enjoyable with your feline companions.</p>
                <small class="text-muted">Published: March 12, 2026</small>
                <br />
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-primary mt-2">Read More</a>
            </div>
        </article>
